      "notes": "The Panther is the 'better than a Tiger' surprise for players who think they know WWII tanks. She's faster, her gun is nearly as deadly, and she's more common. Mechanical reliability is her weakness \u2014 transmission failures were epidemic. Roll for breakdown after sustained high-speed movement.",
