      "desc": "Germany's most produced armoured vehicle. A 75mm gun on a Panzer III chassis with no turret \u2014 she's lower, cheaper, and harder to spot than a proper tank. The StuG fought as assault gun, tank destroyer, and infantry support depending on what the front needed most that day.",
